  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="UI Designer & Frontend developer ~ Sinergias Project"
      subtitle="March 2023 at Bogotá DC, Colombia"
      desc="System multiplatform that includes the steps of a company's personnel, the structure and composition thereof, as well as a powerful designer of credentials and module of control of access. Outspread at the MINFAR and another entities of the country. Technologies: React, Redux, Expressjs, Figma, Notion, NodeJs"
